abstract: Raynette Turner of Mount Vernon, NY, is found dead in holding cell, where she had been awaiting arraignment on shoplifting charge for two days; state authorities are investigating case.
lead_paragraph: Raynette Turner, 42, waited two days in a cell in Mount Vernon, N.Y., for arraignment on a shoplifting arrest.

headline.main: Woman Found Dead in Holding Cell in Westchester County
headline.print_headline: Woman Found Dead in Holding Cell
